Summary: Disc like features with bright lights around the bottom outer rim moving right to left.
divs: Sighting DetailsMy brother and I were walking back from my sisters house that evening. When we were about to cross the street on Edinger and Raitt st. I noticed some lights directly above us. At first I thought it was a blimp or air plane of some sort, but then when I told my brother, we both realized it was not. It had a disc shape look to it, with lights going around the outer bottom rim of the object with a red blinking light on top. I really did not know what to think, it was too real... What I do know is that it was not an airplane, or a helicopter, or a blimp.... One thing I did notice is other people saw it as well and they could not identify it either, they were in shock... it hovered for a few minutes then started moving south south west and finaly went out of sight...
